snippet.title: I tried to make a Horror Game... and ended up with three Horrorgames
snippet.description:
Oh yeah, it's time again to release a new Game! If you want any of the two other games released, write it in the comments :D

If you want to support a Guy who makes Games and loves Capybaras (that's me) consider:
⭐ Subscribing 🔔(Else the racoons will feast on your flesh)
Helping Sophia with the laundry🦝:https://capybaraforge.itch.io/racoonfeast
Checking out Mr. Lupin 🎩: https://capybaraforge.itch.io/mr-lupin
Visiting my First Game's page🐶: https://capybaraforge.itch.io/three-minutes-with-your-dog
Or following my Itch.io account so you don't miss my next Horror Game 🦺🥽 : https://capybaraforge.itch.io/

Markiplier's Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_sZBIWWPFUM&t=817s

Either way, hope you have a wonderful day! :D

Outro:
